quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  28,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  28,1,Taa-Seeen-Meeem
  28,2,yeh kitaab roshan ki ayatain hain
  28,3,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum tumhe moose aur firaon ke kuch halaat momin logon ko sunanay ke liye sahih sahih sunaate hain
  28,4,ke firaon ne malik mein sir uttha rakha tha aur wahan ke bashindon ko giroh giroh bana rakha tha unn mein se aik giroh ko ( yahan taq ) kamzor kar diya tha ke unn ke biton ko zibah kar dalta aur unn ki larkiyon ko zindah rehne deta. bay shak woh mfsdon mein tha
  28,5,aur hum chahtay they ke jo log malik mein kamzor kar diye gay hain unn par ahsaan karen aur unn ko peshwa banayen aur inhen ( malik ka ) waris karen
  28,6,aur malik mein un ko qudrat den aur firaon aur Haman aur unn ke lashkar ko woh cheeze dikha den jis se woh drtay they
  28,7,aur hum ne moose ki maa ki taraf wahi bhaije ke is ko doodh palao jab tum ko is ke baray mein kuch khauf peda ho to usay darya mein daal dena aur nah to khauf karna aur nah ranj karna. hum is ko tumahray paas wapas pouncha den ge aur ( phir ) ussay paighambar bana den ge
  28,8,to firaon ke logon ne is ko uttha liya is liye ke ( nateeja yeh hona tha ke ) woh unn ka dushman aur ( un ke liye mojab ) gham ho. bay shak firaon aur Haman aur unn ke lashkar chowk gay
  28,9,aur firaon ki biwi ne kaha ke ( yeh ) meri aur tumhari ( dono ki ) aankhon ki thandak hai is ko qatal nah karna. shayad yeh hamein faida p_hnchaye ya hum ussay beta banalen aur woh injaam se be khabar they
  28,10,aur moose ki maa ka dil be sabr ho gaya agar hum unn ke dil mazboot nah kar dete to qareeb tha ke woh is ( qsse ) ko zahir kar den. gharz yeh thi ke woh mominoun mein rahen
  28,11,aur is ki behan se kaha ke is ke peechay peechay chali ja to woh ussay daur se dekhatii rahi aur un ( logon ) ko kuch khabar nah thi
  28,12,aur hum ne pehlay hi se is par ( daiyon ) ke doodh haraam kar diye they. to moose ki behan ne kaha ke mein tumhe aisay ghar walay batau ke tumahray liye is ( bachay ) ko paleen aur is ki kher khawahi ( se parwarish ) karen
  28,13,to hum ne ( is tareeq se ) unn ko un ki maa ke paas wapas pouncha diya taakay unn ki ankhen thandhi hon aur woh gham nah khayen aur maloom karen ke khuda ka wada sacha hai lekin yeh aksar nahi jantay
  28,14,aur jab moose jawani ko puhanche aur bharpoor ( jawan ) ho gay to hum ne unn ko hikmat aur ilm inayatkiya. aur hum naiko karon ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  28,15,aur woh aisay waqt shehar mein daakhil hue ke wahan ke bashinday be khabar ho rahay they to dekha ke wahan do shakhs lar rahay they aik to moose ki qoum ka hai aur dosra unn ke dushmanon mein se to jo shakhs unn ki qoum mein se tha is ne dosray shakhs ke muqablay mein jo moose ke dushmanon mein se tha madad talab ki to onhon ne is ko mukka mara aur is ka kaam tamam kar diya kehnay lagey ke yeh kaam to ( aghwa-ay ) shetan se howa bay shak woh ( ensaan ka ) dushman aur Sarih behkanay wala hai
  28,16,bolay ke ae perwar-digaar mein ne apne aap par zulmkiya to mujhe bakhash day to khuda ne unn ko bakhash diya. bay shak woh bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  28,17,kehnay lagey ke ae perwar-digaar to ne jo mujh par meharbani farmai hai mein ( aindah ) kabhi gunahgaaron ka madadgaar nah banon
  28,18,algaraz subah ke waqt shehar mein drtay drtay daakhil hue ke dekhen (kiya hota hai ) to nagahan wohi shakhs jis ne kal unn se madad mangi thi phir unn ko pukaar raha hai. moose ne is se kaha ke too to Sarih gumraah hai
  28,19,jab moose ne iradahkiya ke is shakhs ko jo un dono ka dushman tha pakar len to woh ( yani moose ki qoum ka aadmi ) bol uttha ke jis terhan tum ne kal 1 shakhs ko maar dala tha isi terhan chahtay ho ke mujhe bhi maar daalo. tum to yahi chahtay ho ke malik mein zulm vstm karte phiro aur yeh nahi chahtay ho ke naiko karon mein ho
  28,20,aur 1 shakhs shehar ki parli taraf se dorta howa aaya ( aur ) bola ke moose ( shehar ke ) Raees tumahray baray mein slahaiytain karte hain ke tum ko maar dalain so tum yahan se nikal jao. mein tumhara kher khuwa hon
  28,21,moose wahan se drtay drtay nikal kharray hue ke dekhen (kiya hota hai ) aur dua karne lagey ke ae perwar-digaar mujhe zalim logon se nijaat day .
  28,22,aur jab Mudin ki taraf rukhkiya to kehnay lagey umeed hai ke mera perwar-digaar mujhe seedha rasta betaye
  28,23,aur jab Mudin ke pani ( ke maqam ) par puhanche to dekha ke wahan log jama ho rahay ( aur apne charpayon ko ) pani pila rahay hain aur un ke aik taraf do aurtain ( apni bakrion ko ) rokay khari hain. moose ne ( unn se ) kaha tumharakiya kaam hai. woh bolein ke jab taq charwahay ( apne charpayon ko ) le nah jayen hum pani nahi pila satke aur hamaray waalid barri Umar ke boorhay hain
  28,24,to moose ne unn ke liye ( bakrion ko ) pani pila diya phir saaye ki taraf chalay gay. aur kehnay lagey ke perwar-digaar mein is ka mohtaaj hon ke to mujh par apni Nemat nazil farmaiye
  28,25,( thori der ke baad ) un mein se aik aurat jo sharamati aur lujati chali aati thi. moose ke paas aayi aur kehnay lagi ke tum ko mere waalid bulatay hain ke tum ne jo hamaray liye pani pilaya tha is ki tum ko aُjrt den. jab woh unn ke paas aeye aur unn se apna maajra bayankiya to onhon ne kaha ke kuch khauf nah karo. tum zalim logon se bach aeye ho
  28,26,aik larki boli ke abba un ko nokar rakh lijiye kyunkay behtar nokar jo aap rakhen woh hai ( jo ) tawana aur amanat daar ( ho )
  28,27,onhon ne ( moose se ) kaha ke mein chahta hon apni do baityon mein se aik ko tum se bayah dun is ehad par ke tum aath baras meri khidmat karo aur agar das saal poooray kar do to tumhari taraf se ( ahsaan ) hai aur mein tum par takleef dalni nahi chahta. mujhe Insha allah naik logon mein pao ge
  28,28,moose ne kaha ke mujh mein aur aap mein yeh ( ehad pukhta howa ) mein jonsi muddat ( chahoon ) poori kardoon phir mujh par koi zayad-ti nah ho. aur hum jo moahida karte hain khuda is ka gawah hai
  28,29,jab moose ne muddat poori kar di aur apne ghar ke logon ko le kar chalay to tor ki taraf se aag dikhayi di to apne ghar walon se kehnay lagey ke tum yahan tehro. mujhe aag nazar aayi hai shayad mein wahan se ( raste ka ) kuch pata lau ya aag ka angara le aon taakay tum taapo
  28,30,jab is ke paas puhanche to maidan ke dayen kinare se aik mubarak jagah mein aik darakht mein se aawaz aayi ke moose mein to khuday-e rab alaalmin hon
  28,31,"aur yeh ke apni laathi daal do. jab dekha ke woh harkat kar rahi hai goya saanp hai, to peeth phair kar chal diye aur peechay phir kar bhi nah dekha. ( hum ne kaha ke ) moose agay aao aur daro matt tum aman panay walon mein ho"
  28,32,apna haath garibaan mein daalo to baghair kisi aib ke safaid nikal aeye ga aur khauf daur honay ( ki wajah ) se apne baazu ko apni taraf sukair lo. yeh do daleelen tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se hain ( un ke sath ) firaon aur is ke drbaryon ke paas jao ke woh nafarman log hain
  28,33,moose ne kaha ae perwar-digaar unn mein ka 1 shakhs mere haath se qatal hochuka hai so mujhe khauf hai ke woh ( kahin ) mujh ko maar nah dalain
  28,34,aur Haroon ( jo ) mera bhai ( hai ) is ki zabaan mujh se ziyada Fasih hai to is ko mere sath madadgaar banakar bhaij ke meri tasdeeq kere mujhe khauf hai ke woh meri log takzieeb karen ge
  28,35,( khuda ne ) farmaya hum tumahray bhai se tumahray baazu mazboot karen ge aur tum dono ko ghalba den ge to hamari nshanyon ke sabab woh tum taq poanch nah saken ge ( aur ) tum aur jinhon ne tumhari pairwi ki ghalib raho ge
  28,36,aur jab moose unn ke paas hamari khuli nishanain le kar aeye to woh kehnay lagey ke yeh jaadoo hai jo uss ne bana kharakiya hai aur yeh baatein hum ne apne aglay baap dada mein to ( kabhi ) suni nahi
  28,37,aur moose ne kaha ke mera perwar-digaar is shakhs ko khoob jaanta hai jo is ki taraf se haq le kar aaya hai aur jis ke liye aqibat ka ghar ( yani bahisht ) hai. bay shak zalim nijaat nahi payen ge
  28,38,aur firaon ne kaha ke ae ehley darbaar mein tumhara apne siwa kisi ko khuda nahi jaanta to Haman mere liye gaaray ko aag lagwa ( kar eenten pkwa ) do phir aik ( ooncha ) mehal بنادو taakay mein moose ke khuda ki taraf charh jaoon aur mein to ussay jhoota samjhta hon
  28,39,aur woh aur is ke lashkar malik mein na-haq maghrour ho rahay they aur khayaal karte they ke woh hamari taraf lout kar nahi ayen ge
  28,40,to hum ne unn ko aur unn ke lashkaron ko pakerliya aur darya mein daal diya. so dekh lau zaalmon ka kaisa injaam howa
  28,41,aur hum ne un ko peshwa banaya tha woh ( logon ) ko dozakh ki taraf bulatay they aur qayamat ke din unn ki madad nahi ki jaye gi
  28,42,aur is duniya se hum ne unn ke peechay laanat lagadi aur woh qayamat ke roz bhi بدحالوں mein hon ge
  28,43,aur hum ne pehli amtoN ke halaak karne ke baad moose ko kitaab di jo logon ke liye baseerat aur hadaayat aur rehmat hai taakay woh nasiyaat pakren
  28,44,aur jab hum ne moose ki taraf hukum bheja to tum ( tor ki ) garbh ki taraf nahi they aur nah is waqeye ke dekhnay walon mein they
  28,45,lekin hum ne ( moose ke baad ) kayi amtoN ko pedakiya phir un par muddat taweel guzar gayi aur nah tum Mudin walon mein rehne walay they ke un ko hamari ayatain parh parh kar sunaate they. haan hum hi to paighambar bhejnay walay they
  28,46,aur nah tum is waqt jab ke hum ne ( moose ko ) aawaz di tor ke kinare they balkay ( tumhara bheja jana ) tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat hai taakay tum unn logon ko jin ke paas tum se pehlay koi hadaayat karne wala nahi aaya hadaayat karo taakay woh nasiyaat pakren
  28,47,aur ( ae paighambar hum ne to ko is liye bheja hai ke ) aisa nah ho ke agar un ( aamaal ) ke sabab jo unn ke haath agay bhaij chuke hain un par koi museebat waqay ho to yeh kehnay lagen ke ae perwar-digaar to ne hamari taraf koi paighambar kyun nah bheja ke hum teri aayton ki pairwi karne aur imaan laane walon mein hotay
  28,48,phir jab unn ke paas hamari taraf se haq aap_hncha to kehnay lagey ke jaisi ( nishanain ) moose ko mili theen waisi is ko kyun nahi milein.kiya jo ( nishanain ) pehlay moose ko di gayi theen onhon ne unn se kufar nahikiya. kehnay lagey ke dono jadugar hain aik dosray ke mawafiq. aur bolay ke hum sab se munhkir hain
  28,49,keh do ke agar sachey ho to tum khuda ke paas se koi kitaab le aao jo un dono ( kitabon ) se barh kar hadaayat karne wali ho. taakay mein bhi isi ki pairwi karoon
  28,50,phir agar yeh tumhari baat qubool nah karen to jaan lau ke yeh sirf apni khawahishon ki pairwi karte hain. aur is se ziyada kon gumraah hoga jo khuda ki hadaayat ko chore kar apni khwahish ke peechay chalay. bay shak khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  28,51,aur hum pay darpay unn logon ke paas ( hadaayat ki ) baatein bhaijtay rahay hain taakay nasiyaat pakren
  28,52,jin logon ko hum ne is se pehlay kitaab di thi woh is par imaan le atay hain
  28,53,aur jab ( quran ) unn ko parh kar sunaya jata hai to kehte hain ke hum is par imaan le aeye bay shak woh hamaray perwar-digaar ki taraf se brhq hai aur hum to is se pehlay ke hukambardar hain
  28,54,un logon ko dugna badla diya jaye ga kyunkay sabr karte rahay hain aur bhalai ke sath buraiee ko daur karte hain aur jo ( maal ) hum ne unn ko diya hai is mein se kharch karte hain
  28,55,aur jab behooda baat suntay hain to is se munh phair letay hain aur kehte hain ke hum ko hamaray aamaal aur tum ko tumahray aamaal. tum ko salam. hum jahilon ke khawastgah nahi hain
  28,56,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum jis ko dost rakhtay ho ussay hadaayat nahi kar satke balkay khuda hi jis ko chahta hai hadaayat karta hai aur woh hadaayat panaywalon ko khoob jaanta hai
  28,57,aur kehte hain ke agar hum tumahray sath hadaayat ki pairwi karen to apne malik se uchak liye jayen.kiya hum ne unn ko haram mein jo aman ka maqam hai jagah nahi di. jahan har qisam ke meway p_hnchaye jatay hain ( aur yeh ) rizaq hamari taraf se hai lekin un mein se aksar nahi jantay
  28,58,aur hum ne bohat si bustiyon ko halaak kar dala jo apni ( farakhi ) maeeshat mein Itra rahay they. so yeh unn ke makanaat hain jo unn ke baad abad hi nahi hue magar bohat kam. aur unn ke peechay hum hi unn ke waris hue
  28,59,aur tumhara perwar-digaar bustiyon ko halaak nahikiya karta. jab taq unn ke barray shehar mein paighambar nah bhaij le jo unn ko hamari ayatain parh parh kar sunaye aur hum bustiyon ko halaak nahikiya karte magar is haalat mein ke wahan ke bashinday zalim hon
  28,60,aur jo cheez tum ko di gayi hai woh duniya ki zindagi ka faida aur is ki zeenat hai. aur jo khuda ke paas hai woh behtar aur baqi rehne wali hai.kiya tum samajte nahi ?
  28,61,bhala jis shakhs se hum ne naik wadakiya aur uss ne ussay haasil karliya tokiya woh is shakhs ka sa hai jis ko hum ne duniya ki zindagi ke faiday se behra mandkiya phir woh qayamat ke roz un logon mein ho jo ( hamaray rubaroo ) haazir kiye jayen ge
  28,62,aur jis roz khuda unn ko pukare ga aur kahe ga ke mere woh shareek kahan hain jin ka tumhe daawa tha
  28,63,( to ) jin logon par ( azaab ka ) hukum saabit hochuka hoga woh kahin ge ke hamaray perwar-digaar yeh woh log hain jin ko hum ne gumraahkiya tha. aur jis terhan hum khud gumraah hue they isi terhan unn ko gumraahkiya tha ( ab ) hum teri taraf ( mutwajjah hokar ) unn se bezaar hotay hain yeh hamein nahi pujte they
  28,64,aur kaha jaye ga ke apne sharikon ko bulaao. to woh unn ko pukaarain ge aur woh unn ko jawab nah day saken ge aur ( jab ) azaab ko dekh len ge ( to tamanna karen ge ke ) kash woh hadaayat yab hotay
  28,65,aur jis roz khuda unn ko pukare ga aur kahe ga ke tum ne payghambaroon kokiya jawab diya
  28,66,"to woh is roz khabron se andhay ho jayen ge, aur aapas mein kuch bhi pooch nah saken ge"
  28,67,lekin jis ne tauba ki aur imaan laya aur amal naik kiye to umeed hai ke woh nijaat panay walon mein ho
  28,68,aur tumhara perwar-digaar jo chahta hai peda karta hai aur ( jisay chahta hai ) bargzida karleta hai. un ko is ka ikhtiyar nahi hai. yeh jo shirk karte hain khuda is se pak o balater hai
  28,69,aur un ke seenay jo kuch makhfi karte aur jo yeh zahir karte hain tumhara perwar-digaar is ko jaanta hai
  28,70,aur wohi khuda hai is ke siwa koi mabood nahi duniya aur akhirat mein usi ki tareef hai aur usi ka hukum aur isi ki taraf tum lout’tay jao ge
  28,71,kaho bhala dekho to agar khuda tum par hamesha qayamat ke din taq raat ( ki tareqi ) kiye rahay to khuda ke siwa kon mabood hai hai jo tum ko roshni laa day tokiya tum suntay nahi ?
  28,72,kaho to bhala dekho to agar khuda tum par hamesha qayamat taq din kiye rahay to khuda ke siwa kon mabood hai ke tum ko raat laa day jis mein tum aaraam karo. tokiya tum dekhte nahi ?
  28,73,aur is ne apni rehmat se tumahray liye raat ko aur din ko banaya taakay tum is mein aaraam karo aur is mein is ka fazl talaash karo aur taakay shukar karo
  28,74,aur jis din woh unn ko pukare ga aur kahe ga ke mere woh shareek jin ka tumhe daawa tha kahan gay ?
  28,75,aur hum har aik aُmt mein se gawah nikaal len ge phir kahin ge ke apni Daleel paish karo to woh jaan len ge ke sach baat khuda ki hai aur jo kuch woh iftirakiya karte they un se jata rahay ga
  28,76,qaroon moose ki qoum mein se tha aur un par ta-adi karta tha. aur hum ne is ko itnay khazanay diye they ke unn ki knjyan aik taaqatwar jamaat ko uthani mushkil hoten jab is se is ki qoum ne kaha ke atraiyay mat. ke khuda itranay walon ko pasand nahi karta
  28,77,aur jo ( maal ) tum ko khuda ne ataa farmaya hai is se akhirat ki bhalai talab kijiyej aur duniya se apna hissa nah bhulaiyay aur jaisi khuda ne tum se bhalai ki hai ( waisi ) tum bhi ( logon se ) bhalai karo. aur malik mein taalib fasaad nah ho. kyunkay khuda fasaad karne walon ko dost nahi rakhta
  28,78,bola ke yeh ( maal ) mujhe meri Danish ( ke zor ) se mila haikiya is ko maloom nahi ke khuda ne is se pehlay bohat si ummatain jo is se qowat mein barh kar aur jamiat mein beshtar theen halaak kar daali hain. aur gunahgaaron se unn ke gunaaho ke baray mein poocha nahi jaye ga
  28,79,to ( aik roz ) qaroon ( barri ) Araish ( aur thaath ) se apni qoum ke samnay nikla. jo log duniya ki zindagi ke taalib they kehnay lagey ke jaissa ( maal o mata'a) qaroon ko mila hai kash aisa hi hamein bhi miley. woh to bara hi sahib naseeb hai
  28,80,aur jin logon ko ilm diya gaya tha woh kehnay lagey ke tum par afsos. mominoun aur naiko karon ke liye ( jo ) sawab khuda ( ke haan tayyar hai woh ) kahin behtar hai aur woh sirf sabr karne walon hi ko miley ga
  28,81,pas hum ne qaroon ko aur is ke ghar ko zameen mein dhansa diya to khuda ke siwa koi jamaat is ki madadgaar nah hosaki. aur nah woh badla le saka
  28,82,aur woh log jo kal uss ke rutbey ki tamanna karte they subah ko kehnay lagey haae shamat! khuda hi to apne bundon mein se jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq farakh kar deta hai aur ( jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kar deta hai. agar khuda hum par ahsaan nah karta to hamein bhi dhansa deta. haae kharabi! kafir nijaat nahi pa satke
  28,83,woh ( jo ) akhirat ka ghar ( hai ) hum ne ussay unn logon ke liye ( tayyar ) kar rakha hai jo malik mein zulm aur fasaad ka iradah nahi rakhtay aur injaam ( naik ) to parhaiz garon hi ka hai
  28,84,jo shakhs neki le kar aeye ga is ke liye is se behtar ( sila mojood ) hai aur jo buraiee laaye ga to jin logon ne buray kaam kiye un ko badla bhi isi terhan ka miley ga jis terhan ke woh kaam karte they
  28,85,( ae paighambar ) jis ( khuda ) ne tum par quran ( ke ehkaam ) ko farzkiya hai woh tumhe baaz gasht ki jagah lota day ga. keh do ke mera perwar-digaar is shakhs ko bhi khoob jaanta hai jo hadaayat le kar aaya aur ( is ko bhi ) jo Sarih gumraahi mein hai
  28,86,aur tumhe umeed nah thi ke tum par kitaab nazil ki jaye gi. magar tumahray perwar-digaar ki meharbani se ( nazil hui ) to tum hargiz kafiroon ke madadgaar nah hona
  28,87,aur woh tumhe khuda ki aayton ki tableegh se baad is ke ke woh tum par nazil hochuki hain rok nah den aur apne perwar-digaar ko pkarte raho aur mushrikon mein hargiz nah ho geo
  28,88,aur khuda ke sath kisi aur ko mabood ( samajh kar ) nah pukarna is ke siwa koi mabood nahi. is ki zaat ( pak ) ke siwa har cheez fanaa honay wali hai. isi ka hukum hai aur isi ki taraf tum lout kar jao ge
